# Local development secrets for `wrangler dev`.
# Copy to `.dev.vars` (gitignored) and fill in. In production these are set with
# `wrangler secret put <NAME>` instead of living in this file.

# Authorizes first-party API-key administration (issue / list / revoke) on
# /api/keys. Pick a long random value, e.g. `openssl rand -hex 32`.
ADMIN_TOKEN="replace-with-a-long-random-string"

# Optional: Lemon Squeezy hosted checkout URL for the Pro upgrade button.
# LEMONSQUEEZY_CHECKOUT_URL="https://your-store.lemonsqueezy.com/buy/..."
